WEBVTT

00:00:06.669 --> 00:00:11.669
is living without pain or sadness possible.

00:00:11.669 --> 00:00:18.420
The Bible says that very soon,

00:00:18.420 --> 00:00:22.420
God will wipe out every tear from their eyes

00:00:22.420 --> 00:00:25.420
and death will be no more.

00:00:25.420 --> 00:00:28.420
Neither will morning or outcry,

00:00:28.420 --> 00:00:30.420
nor pain be anymore.

00:00:30.420 --> 00:00:38.280
To learn more about this happy future,

00:00:38.280 --> 00:00:41.280
explore JW.org.
